cs|4|at|^-{ The opening lead of an Ace against a notrump contract asks for the partner of the 
 opening leader to play an honor card if possible and to otherwise give a count signal. }
|
pg| ***** 27 ***** |


nt|^b@2^z@3We just saw how, when the opening leader against notrump is dealt a very strong holding headed by the Ace-King, it will be helpful to him if his partner plays an honor card under his lead of the Ace. |
