nt|^b@2^z@3In almost all of the examples of attitude signals that we have seen so far, both discouraging and encouraging signals carry a message about the suit of the signal itself (typically as to whether or not the signaler holds a relevant honor card in that suit). When your partner leads a King against a notrump contract, the nature of the message of the attitude signal that you give is slightly different.|
